A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence, wanda ke nufin inganta haɗin gwiwa tsakanin masana'antu da ilimi kuma Shugaban Amurka ya ba da sanarwar kafa Kwamitin Kula da Ilimin Artificial.
