A lokacin da aka fara yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia, a tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi watsi da yakin neman zabensa a cikin hadari a cikin Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shine farkon kamfen din Trump na biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da yin zango a wurare da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ba a gudanar da zaben tabbatar da wanda ya zaba a matsayin shugaban kotun koli ba, Trump yana neman taimako a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa tunda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a kan Majalisar a zaben Nuwamba.
Yaushe za a gudanar da yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a daren yau kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya bikin kamfen na Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na dare ET, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a hanyar haɗin yanar gizo na YouTube.
Ana iya ganin Trump zai yi magana ne a zaman kotun koli na wannan makon game da wanda aka zaba a matsayin shugaban kotun kolin kasar, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya karu saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i wanda aka dage zaben majalisar dattijai saboda binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin yakin neman zaben shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su ci gaba da samun karfin gwiwa a babban zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, jami'an yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce yakin neman zabe guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa suna da nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da masu adawa yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma bunkasa rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", a cewar rahoton Reuters.
Wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump ya bukaci Reuters ta rubuta: "Sarrafa majalisar wakilai wani muhimmin bangare ne na shirinsa don shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke tafiya zuwa lokacin yakin neman zabe".
An shirya gudanar da yakin neman zabe a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, wanda zai iya jawo masu fafutuka daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun rahoto daga Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, wannan ita ce ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata zuwa West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican daga jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey ya zama shugaban kasa wanda ya kamata ya zo don taimaka masa ya sami ƙarin kuri'u", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cikin wata hira da Reuters.
