Fleetwood ya zama dan wasa na farko na Turai da ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan wani mako mai ban sha'awa, su ne kawai 'yan wasa biyu da suka ci kwallaye hudu a wasanni hudu na farko a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup.
Gasar da ya yi da Woods da Patrick Reed a wasa na hudu ta sa ya yi nasara da Woods wanda ba shi da kyau da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau wanda ya ci gaba da samun maki 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya buga wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna kyakkyawan wasan amma yanzu ya rasa wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 da ya buga a wasanni hudu da wasanni hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda bai buga wasan ba a wasan farko na wasan farko na wasan farko, ya maye gurbin abokin karawarsa Henrik Stenson a wasan na hudu lokacin da suka sha kashi 2&1 a hannun Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, wadanda ke kan gaba a jerin sunayen duniya.
Turai ba ta yi wasa kamar yadda ta saba ba, ta yi wasa da farin ciki, ranar da iska ta yi ta fitowa daga kudu maso yammacin Paris.
An nada Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, wadanda suka lashe manyan kofuna uku, a matsayin masu farawa biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci 2&1 a kan 'yan Spain Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan da aka buga hudu kuma sun dawo daga baya sun ci Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a wasan na hudu bayan an doke su a ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup ne kawai aka ci nasara a kan 'yan wasa hudu a jere, duk da cewa masu rike da kofin Furyk suna bukatar su ci gaba da zama daidai don riƙe kofin.
Bayan sun kasance 'yan mata masu kyau a cikin kwanaki biyu, amma yanzu a ranar Lahadi za su yi wasan da za su rama duk da cewa za su yi nasara.
