Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa jami'an kasa a babban taron shekara-shekara cewa an dauki "matakai masu mahimmanci" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya, lalata wuraren gwajin makaman nukiliya da tabbatar da cewa ba a ci gaba da kera makaman nukiliya da fasahar makaman nukiliya ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga amsar da Amurka za ta bayar ba", in ji shi.
"Babu wata hanyar da Amurka za ta iya amincewa da tsaron ƙasashenmu kuma idan haka ne babu yadda za mu iya kasancewa ƙasa ɗaya da za ta daina yin makaman nukiliya".
Yayin da Ri ya sake maimaita zargin da Koriya ta Arewa ke yi game da matakin da Washington ke dauka na "tsari" na dakatar da kera makaman nukiliya inda Koriya ta Arewa za ta iya sarrafa farashin yayin da take ci gaba, maganganun nasa sun yi kama da inganci duk da cewa bai musanta yiwuwar Pyongyang ta daina kera makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda ta yi a baya.
Ri ya biyo bayan jawabin da Shugabannin biyu Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko na shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi fatan yin aiki don "dakatar da aikin nukiliya a yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin kare tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na son kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara dakatar da kera makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta ki amincewa da sassauta takunkumin da ta kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Ya ce: "Amurka ta ci gaba da dagewa kan cewa 'da farko mu daina yin makaman nukiliya' kuma ta kara matsa lamba ta hanyar sanya takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar amfani da karfi, duk da kin amincewa da 'ƙaddamar da ƙarshen yaƙi.'"
"Tunanin cewa azabtarwa na iya sa mu durƙusa a ƙasa mafarki ne mai ban mamaki ga al'ummomin da ke watsi da mu.
Amma matsalar ita ce, yawan takunkumi yana sa mu ƙara amincewa da su".
Ri bai ce komai ba game da shirin taron karawa juna sani na Kim da Trump wanda shugaban Amurka ya tattauna a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya ambaci ganawa uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu, Moon Jae-in, a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya ce: "Idan kasar da ke kula da batun tsagaita makaman nukiliya ita ce Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, to tsagaita makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya ba zai tsaya ba".
Kuma, sautin Ri ya bambanta da na shekara mai zuwa, lokacin da ya yi magana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa yunƙurin harba makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Kudu zuwa Amurka zai yiwu bayan "Majin Shugaban da ke da mummunan buri" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin da ke yin bam na kai hari" wanda ke shirin kashe kansa.
A taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na wannan shekara, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda matakin da ya dauka na dakatar da kera makamai masu linzami, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi da kuma takunkumin da za a ci gaba da sanyawa har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta daina kera makamai masu linzami.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin yin hakan, yana cewa "Idan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, uku ko watanni uku; ba matsala".
China da Rasha sun yi ta takaddama kan bukatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ba da lada ga gwamnatin Pyongyang saboda matakin da ta dauka.
Koyaya, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da tsaurara takunkumin Kwamitin Tsaro cikin ƙarfi da ƙarfi har sai an tabbatar da cewa an kawar da makaman nukiliya gaba ɗaya, cikin sauri da kuma a hankali".
Kwamitin Tsaro ya yanke shawarar ba da izini ba don tsawaita takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun daga 2006 don hana tallafin da Pyongyang ke bayarwa don shirin nukiliyar ta da makaman roket.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wani taron da aka yi a wani bangare na taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma daga baya ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar da ya yi kwanan nan ba ta yi nasara ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an yi wani mataki, amma bayan 'yan sa'o'i Koriya ta Arewa ta musanta wannan da'awar ta bayyana cewa "buƙatun sun yi kama da na 'yan fashi".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a ganawar da ta yi da Moon cewa za ta lalata masana'antar kera makamai masu linzami da kuma tashoshin nukiliya a wannan watan idan Amurka ta "yi irin wannan matakin".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake so su kasance na tabbatar da tsaro a karkashin yarjejeniyar da Trump ya bayar a Singapore kuma yana ci gaba da inganta dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Jami'ar Harvard suna koyon darussan hutawa sosai.
Wani sabon binciken da Jami'ar Harvard ta gabatar a wannan shekara ya ba da damar samun karin bacci ga duk daliban da ba su kammala karatun digiri na biyu ba don magance karuwar maza na shan maganin kafeyin da kuma yin nazari 'duk dare'.
Wani jami'in jami'a ya gano cewa ɗaliban da ke kan gaba a jami'a ɗaya ba su da cikakken bayani game da yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da na mata, ya tsara darasin, wanda ya yi imanin shine farkon irin wannan shiri a Amurka.
Ya ba da shawarar fara darasin bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
'A ƙarshen tattaunawar, wata yarinya ta zo wurina kuma ta ce, 'Me ya sa za ki gaya mini wannan yanzu, tun da ina shekara ta ƙarshe a makarantar sakandare?'
Ya ce ba wanda ya taɓa gaya masa muhimmancin barci, abin mamaki ne a gare ni,' in ji ta ga jaridar The Telegraph.
Darasin, wanda aka fara bayarwa, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai abubuwan yau da kullun cewa samun isasshen barci yana taimakawa ɗalibai da 'yan wasa suyi aiki da kyau, kuma yana inganta ƙoshin lafiya gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar kwakwalwa a Harvard Medical School kuma babban daraktan jami'ar a fannin kula da kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da darasin ne bayan dalibai sun shafe mako guda ba sa barci.
Darasin na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka da yawa na sadarwa.
A wani bangare akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke latsa kofi, labule, takalman motsa jiki da littattafai kuma ana gaya musu tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske shine yadda rashin bacci yake shafar wasan kwaikwayo da kuma mahimmancin al'adun bacci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa mahalarta binciken cewa rashin barci na dogon lokaci na iya kara hadarin cututtukan zuciya, bugun jini, damuwa, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar kwaleji, tare da zane-zane masu ban sha'awa, yana ƙarfafa masu halarta su yi tunani game da abin da suke yi a kan lokaci.
'Mun san cewa ba za su iya canza halin ɗalibai nan da nan ba.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ce: "Amma mun yi imani suna da 'yancin sanin; kamar yadda kuke da 'yancin sanin sakamakon shan taba".
Ya ce: "Har yanzu akwai al'adar da ke nuna damuwa game da karatun 'dare'," ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani tana kara matsa lamba ga dalibai wanda ke nufin rashin bacci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Ganin cewa suna samun isasshen, ingantaccen bacci, ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' ga ɗalibai don magance damuwa, damuwa da damuwa; da kuma hana kiba, saboda rashin bacci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana sa ta zama cikin yunwa.
Raymond So, dalibi mai shekaru 19 a California wanda ke nazarin ilimin halittu da ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler shirya darasin, saboda ya yi karatun sa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekarar farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe idanunsa kuma ya sa ya so a koyar da shi a dukan jami'a.
Ya yi imanin cewa mataki na gaba shi ne a bukaci daliban da suka kammala karatun digiri na biyu su kammala wasu shirye-shirye kafin su shiga cibiyoyin neman aiki.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai suyi la'akari da sanya alamun lokacin kwantawa da lokacin farkawa da kuma abubuwan haɗari kamar hasken shuɗi na kayan aikin lantarki da fitilun LED, wanda zai iya sa ku tashi cikin damuwa yayin da kuke barci, yana haifar da matsalolin bacci.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Kwallan Menga ya ci wa 'yan wasan Gerrard da suka yi nasara
Rangers sun sake yin kwallo a ido inda Dolly Menga ta doke Steven Gerrard da ci 1-0 a Livingston.
Ita dai kungiyar Ibrox ta yi ta neman nasarar farko tun bayan da St Johnstone ta doke ta da ci 4-1 a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holt ya doke Gerrard a karo na biyu cikin wasanni 18 a matsayin shugaban kungiyar domin sa ta kasance a baya a gasar Ladbrokes a bayan Hearts.
Menga ya ci kwallo a raga da minti bakwai kafin a kammala wasan farko inda Rangers suka ci gaba da zama masu tsaron gida.
Yayin da Rangers ta koma ta shida, Livingston ya tashi zuwa na uku kuma yana baya da Hibernian a kan ragamar ci.
Kuma akwai yiwuwar wasu matsaloli da ke jiran Rangers bayan da aka gano cewa alkalin wasa na gefe, Calum Spence, ya ji rauni a kai bayan wani abu da ya bayyana a matsayin mai nisa.
Gerrard ya yi sauye-sauye takwas a tawagarsa a wasan da suka yi da Ayr domin samun damar shiga wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin duniya.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt, wanda ya dauki 'yan Livi 11 da suka ci Hearts a makon da ya gabata, ya yi farin ciki da yadda kungiyar ta kori abokan karawarsu a duk wasan.
Rangers na iya zama masu ƙwarewa sosai a wasan amma Livingston ya samar da ƙarancin ƙwallon ƙafa da suka samu.
Haka kuma, 'yan wasan sun yi nasara a minti kadan lokacin da Menga ya fara buga kwallo ta hanyar Scott Pittman zuwa tsaron Allan McGregor amma dan wasan tsakiya ya sami damar buga kwallon daga waje.
Keaghan Jacobs ya jefa kwallon da aka buga a cikin tsaro wanda ya kai ga mai tsaron gida, Craig Halkett, amma dan wasan baya Alan Lithgow ya jefa kwallon a waje da tsaro.
Rangers sun jagoranci wasan amma kamar dai suna da wani abu da zasu yi fiye da fatan da aka ba su a cikin kashi na uku na ƙarshe.
Babu shakka Alfredo Morelos ya ji ya cancanci hukuncin kisa a minti saba'in da biyar lokacin da ya yi wasa da Steven Lawless amma alkalin wasa, Steven Thomson, ya ƙi amincewa da matakin da ɗan Colombia ya ɗauka.
Rangers sun samu nasarar jefa kwallo biyu ne kawai a raga a zagayen farko amma tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox Liam Kelly bai yi kasa a gwiwa ba sakamakon bugun da Lassana Coulibaly ya yi da kuma bugun da Ovie Ejaria ya yi.
Yayin da Livi ya ci kwallo ta farko a minti na 34 da ya yi, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa ya kamata ya ci kwallo ta hanyar da aka tsara.
Rangers sun sake kasa dawo da kwallon da Jacobs ya buga.
Scott Arfield bai taɓa ƙwallo da Declan Gallagher ya jefa ba kuma ya ba Scott Robinson, wanda bai yi wani abu ba don dakatar da ƙwallo da aka samu cikin sauƙi a tsaron da Menga ya yi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu lokacin da ya sauya Coulibaly zuwa Ryan Kent, wanda ya kusan haifar da sakamako na gaggawa lokacin da aka ba Morelos kwallon daga gaban amma Kelly ya yi tsere sosai kuma ya dakatar da kwallon.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da yin tsayayya da wasan da ya buga a wasan da Lithgow da Halkett suka buga a kai a kai.
Holt ya sake zura kwallo a minti na karshe amma McGregor ya tsaya tsayin daka ya hana Jacobs buga kwallo lokacin da Lithgow ya buga kwallo.
Rangers sun maye gurbin Glenn Middleton wanda ya yi magana game da hukuncin kisa a wasan da suka yi da Jacobs amma alkalin wasa Thomson ya yi watsi da hakan.
Almanac: Wanda ya kirkiro Geiger Counter
Har ma a shafinmu na "Sunday Morning" Almanac: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, kwanaki 136 da suka wuce a yau kuma har yanzu muna tunawa... ranar da aka haifi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanyar ganowa da kuma auna fitar da kwayoyin cuta, wanda ya haifar da kayan aiki da ake kira Geiger Counter.
An kafa shi a matsayin tushen kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger Counter ya zama tushen kayan wasan kwaikwayo, kamar fim ɗin 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya nuna Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Miji: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wani Geiger Counter ne, wanda ake amfani da shi don gano duwatsu masu daraja waɗanda ke da ƙwayoyin cuta kamar uranium.
Idan ka ba ni wannan equator, za ka iya jin sauyin atomatik da ke fitowa daga kwayoyin cuta a cikin duwatsu masu daraja. "
Evans: "A wasu kalmomi, suna tsallewa!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
