Alurar riga kafi tana horar da rigakafin jiki don gane ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa a matsayin ɓangare na maganin.
Wannan hanyar tana cire kwayoyin da ke taimakawa wajen gina rigakafi daga mai haƙuri kuma a canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje
Don haka, suna iya gano furotin da ake samu a yawancin cututtukan daji kuma su sake saka shi cikin jiki.
Wani allurar rigakafin da ake gwadawa tana nuna sakamako mai ban sha'awa ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da cututtukan daji daban-daban.
Wata mace da aka yi wa allurar rigakafi, wadda ke horar da rigakafi don gano ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa, ta warkar da cutar kansa ta mahaifa bayan watanni 18.
A cikin wannan hanyar, ana cire kwayoyin daga mai haƙuri kuma ana canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don "gano" furotin HER2 wanda aka samo a yawancin cututtukan daji kuma a sake saka su cikin jiki.
"Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa muna da allurar rigakafi mai matukar alkawura", in ji Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Kwayar cutar Kansar ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland.
Farfesa Berzofsky ya bayyana cewa HER2 "yana haifar da ci gaban nau'ikan cututtukan daji da yawa", gami da ciwon nono, na mahaifa, na huhu da na tarin fuka.
An yi amfani da wata hanyar da za a cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga mai haƙuri kuma a "koyar" da kwayoyin don kai hari ga ƙwayoyin cutar kansa don magance cutar sankarar bargo.
