Jarumin wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya yi tir da munanan halayen kibo.
Kit Harington ya shahara da yin amfani da takobi a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin jerin fina-finai na HBO Game of Thrones.
Amma dan wasan, mai shekara 31, ya yi tir da nuna bambanci da ake yi wa jarumin da ke nuna namiji, yana mai cewa wasan kwaikwayon yana nuna cewa matasa galibi suna jin cewa dole ne su ci gaba da kasancewa da mutunci.
A wata hira da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ta ce ta yi imanin cewa 'wani abu ya faru ba daidai ba' kuma ta yi mamakin yadda za ta magance matsalar rashin mutuncin maza yayin da aka kafa kamfen din #Me.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasan kwaikwayo ta Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin 'ƙarfin iko' game da magance matsalar.
'Ina jin kaina yana da ƙarfi yanzu,' in ji ta, 'Ina mummunan halin namiji ya fito?
'Shin za mu koya wa maza lokacin da suka girma game da matsalolin da muke fuskanta a yau?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na haɓaka halayen maza saboda 'yan wasan kwaikwayo suna nuna halayen maza.
Ya ci gaba: "Me ya sa aka haifi mutum, me ya sa aka koya masa?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin da kuma a kan titi, da ke sa matasa su ji cewa suna da wani abu da ke sa su zama maza?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya a wannan lokaci: Ta yaya za mu canza wannan?
Domin akwai wani abu da ba daidai ba da matasa suke yi.'
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai iya yin fim din da ke gaba ko bayan Game of Thrones ba lokacin da wasan ya ƙare a wannan bazarar, yana mai cewa 'ba ya son yaƙi da doki.'
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai yi aiki a cikin sabon fim na Sam Shepard mai suna True West wanda shine labarin fim tare da ɗan'uwansa ɓarawo.
Actor din ya bayyana kwanan nan cewa ya ga haduwa da matarsa, Rose, shine mafi kyawun abu daga wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
Ya ce: "Na sadu da matata a wani fim, kuma hakan ya ba ni iyalina na gaba da kuma sabuwar rayuwata daga yanzu".
Rose ta yi wasa da Ygritte, ƙaunataccen Kit wanda Jon Snow ya yi wasa, a cikin jerin shirye-shiryen da aka ba da lambar yabo ta Emmy.
Sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ce an samu karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin dari
China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14% na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da cutar kanjamau.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, a cewar jami'an lafiya.
Kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 aka bayar da rahoton kamuwa da cutar a farkon rabin shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar sun kamu ne ta hanyar saduwa da mutane, wanda ya bambanta da yadda ya kasance a baya.
A wasu sassa na kasar Sin, cutar kanjamau tana yaduwa cikin sauri ta hanyar bayar da jini mai cutar.
Amma yawan kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, in ji hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da kuma wadanda ke fama da cutar AIDS a kasar Sin na karuwa da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga masu yin jima'i da maza a China.
An dakatar da aikata laifuka na luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna wariya ga masu luwadi na kara karuwa.
A cikin al'ummar da ke da al'ada, bincike ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90% na maza masu yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure.
Yawancin cututtukan da ke tattare da cutar suna faruwa ne ta hanyar yin jima'i ba tare da kiyayewa ba.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta tabbatar da samar da maganin cutar kanjamau a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani jami'in majalisar dattijai na Republican ya yi watsi da 'ƙarya mai rikitarwa' da kuma 'ƙulla makirci'
A ranar Asabar, wakilin majalisar wakilai na Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinsa ya wallafa bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican a shafukan majalisa a shafin Wikipedia.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat a Los Angeles ya ce masu gudanar da muhawara da ke "goyon bayan 'yan Republican" sun yi watsi da wannan matakin.
Waters ya bayyana hakan a cikin wani sakon Twitter cewa: "Karya, karya, karya ce mai ban tsoro".
Bayanai da aka bayar sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Rahotanni da aka wallafa a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, an bayyana su ne ta hanyar wani wanda ba a san ko wane ba a kan Capitol Hill a yayin da ake sauraron karar da majalisar dattawa ta gabatar kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Rahotanni sun fito ne bayan da wasu sanatoci uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Hill ya ba da rahoto: Gaskiya shafukan yanar gizo kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun bayyana cewa adireshin IP ɗin da aka nuna a cikin bayanan yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da labarin wani ma'aikacin Waters.
Watera ya ci gaba da cewa: "Waɗannan zarge-zargen ba su da tushe kuma ba gaskiya ba ne, ƙarya ce kawai".
"Wani ma'aikacina, wanda ke da mutuncinsa, bayanansa da amincinsa sun kasance cikin hadari saboda zargin da ake yi na zamba da kuma karya; ba shi da alhakin fitar da wannan bayanin.
Waɗannan zargin ba su da tushe kuma ba gaskiya ba ne, ƙarya ce kawai".
Kalaman Waters sun jawo mummunan zargi a shafukan yanar gizo, gami da sukar tsohon Sakataren yada labarai na fadar shugaban Amurka, Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana da ban haushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da sha'awar zama memba na majalisar.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, kada ya yi fushi.
Bai kamata ya yi hamayya da ikon da yake da shi ba.
Bai kamata ya yi tambaya game da dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumarsa ba.
Ya kamata ya yi shiru kuma ya yi shiru".
Fleischer ya tilasta wa Waters ya kwatanta yadda ya amsa zargin da cewa 'yan Democrat sun soki Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar sa suka zargi da nuna fushinsa a zaman kotun ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Jamhuriyar Republican da ke neman tsige Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya kuma yi tsokaci a shafin Twitter.
"Zai zama da wuya idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi a shafinsa na Twitter.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya sanar da "hukumomi da hukumomin tilasta yin doka da ke binciken abin da ya ce yaudara ce.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano wadanda suka aikata wannan abu", in ji shi, "kuma za a dauki alhakin duk wani aiki da suka yi na lalata ko cutar da ma'aikatan da ke aiki da ni".
Binciken Johnny English Strikes Again - Rowan Atkinson wanda ba shi da ƙarfi ya yi fim a matsayin ɗan wasa
Yanzu, ya zama al'ada a yi la'akari da fa'idar ficewar Burtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai, wanda ya zama kamar sabon fim ne game da Burtaniya kuma yana da alama cewa sabon fim ɗin na jerin fina-finai ne na Johnny English wanda ya fara a 2003 da Johnny English sannan kuma ya sake fitowa a 2011 da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin fim din wasan kwaikwayo ne mai ban dariya akan batun da ba zai iya nuna damarmu a matsayinmu na ƙasa ba game da damar fitarwa?
A kowane hali, tsoho, mai tsufa, ɗan wasan kwaikwayo Johnny English ya sami izinin sake yin fim na biyu, wanda sunansa ya fi dacewa da shi a matsayin babban wasan kwaikwayo na ban dariya ga waɗanda ba sa jin Turanci a cikin al'ummomin da ke kallon fina-finai.
A matsayin jarumi mai ban dariya, yana yin wasan kwaikwayon Clouseau, wanda ya zama kamar Mr. Bean, wanda ya kai ga wani abu mai ban mamaki kamar bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London.
A asali, an kafa shi ne bisa al'ada da kuma wani mutum mai ban mamaki mai suna Atkinson wanda ya taka rawa a wani tallace-tallace na Barclaycard TV wanda yanzu ya zama abin ƙyama, yana haifar da rikici.
Akwai yanayi biyu masu kyau a cikin JE.
Na ji daɗin yadda Johnny English ya kusanci helikofta a cikin rigar soja ta 500 da kuma takobin helikofta mai kaifi wanda ya ɗan taɓa abin da yake sakawa.
Atkinson baiwa ce ta wasan kwaikwayo ta jiki, amma dariya tana da rauni kuma ba ta da kyau a cikin yanayin tashin hankali na yau da kullun kamar shahararrun fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible inda 'yan wasan kwaikwayo "masu sani" suke yin wasan kwaikwayo na kansu a matsayin ƙari.
Baƙon ya zama kamar ga yara ne maimakon manya kuma ayyukan Johnny English na ban mamaki ba su da ƙwarewa kuma suna mai da hankali ne akan finafinan Atkinson inda ba ya faɗin kalma ɗaya a matsayin Bean.
Labarin da aka fi ji shi ne cewa ƙasar Ingila tana cikin haɗari.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin babbar kungiyar leken asiri ta Burtaniya, ya bayyana bayanan duk jami'an leken asiri na Burtaniya da ke aiki a wurare daban-daban, inda aka nuna wani ɗan wasan da ke aiki amma abin takaici an ba shi ɗan ƙaramin rawa mai suna Kevin Eldon.
Wannan ita ce babbar matsalar da ke fuskantar Firayim Minista mai girman kai da adawa, wanda ke cikin halin da zai iya zama ɗan siyasa mara kyau: Emma Thompson tana da kyakkyawan rawar da za ta taka kamar Teresa-May amma ba ta da wani abu mai kyau a cikin rawar da za ta taka.
Masu ba shi shawara a harkokin leken asirinsa sun gaya masa cewa an sanya leken asiri a ko'ina, kuma yana da muhimmanci cewa wani ya yi ritaya.
Kuma wannan yana nufin cewa babu wani sai Johnny English, wanda a halin yanzu yana da aiki a wata makarantar sakandare mai tsada, amma yana ba da darussan da ba na yau da kullun ba inda yake koyar da yadda ake yin leken asiri: Wannan shawara ce mai kyau cewa English yana ba da darasi a makarantar Rock School game da leken asiri.
An mayar da Ingilishi zuwa gidan Whitehall inda dole ne ya sami umarni na gaggawa da sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bough, wanda aka sake buga shi da Ben Miller.
Yanzu, Bough tana da ciki kuma ta auri wani kyaftin jirgin ruwa mai saukar ungulu, wanda Vicki Pepperdine ke yi amma ba ta da amfani.
Don haka Batman da Robin suna wasa da abubuwa masu ban tsoro a cikin Sarauniya ta Sirrin Sirri, suna haɗuwa da wata mace mai tsananin aiki ga Olga Kurylenko mai suna Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Ministan tsaro na kasar ya fada cikin tarkon wani mai fasaha mai kudi da ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalar kwamfuta a Burtaniya: wani dan kasuwa mai suna Jason Volta, mai shan giya tare da Jake Lacy.
Turanci ya fara tafiya mai wuya a cikin ɓoyewa: Ya zama mai ba da sabis, yana aiki a gidan abinci na Faransa; ya haifar da rikici ta hanyar ƙoƙarin shiga cikin jirgin ruwa mai tsada na Volta; kuma Turanci ya yi ƙoƙarin yin abubuwa a hanyarsa ta hanyar ƙoƙarin amfani da takaddun shaida na gaskiya don yin aiki a cikin gidan Volta.
Dukkanin waɗannan abubuwa suna cikin fim ɗin, amma kamar yadda suke da ban sha'awa da ƙarfi, akwai talabijin na yara wanda ke nuna duk wannan.
Hakan ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Kuma kamar yadda sauran fina-finan Johnny English suke, ina tunanin: Shin masana'antar fim a Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson abokin hamayyar da ta fi dacewa ba don nuna basirarta?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana tunanin shirin da za a bai wa 'yan Birtaniya na kwanaki hudu na aiki a mako da kuma biyan su kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn tana tunanin wani babban shiri wanda zai bar duk 'yan Burtaniya su yi aiki kwanaki hudu a mako, amma a biya su kwanaki biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su nemi hanyoyin da za su iya adana kuɗi ta hanyar haɓaka ƙwarewar kere kere (AI) don ma'aikata don samun ƙarin ranar hutu.
Zai iya barin ma'aikata suna jin daɗin ƙarshen mako na kwana uku, amma ana biyan su daidai da yadda aka biya su.
Masu ruwa da tsaki sun ce wannan shawara "ta dace" da manufar jam'iyyar tattalin arziki kuma tana nufin kawo sauyi ga ma'aikatan kasar.
An yi amfani da sauye-sauyen sau hudu a mako wanda Majalisar Kungiyar Kwadago ta tallafawa a matsayin wata hanya ta samar da ma'aikata don yin aiki da canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a fitar da nazarin shirin kafin karshen shekara.
'Ba wani abu bane da zai faru a rana daya amma aiki kwana hudu a mako shine burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma manufofin jam'iyyar a masana'antar gabaɗaya.'
Labour ba zata kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, jam'iyyar kare muhalli ta yi alkawarin samar da aikin kwana hudu a mako a wani babban kamfen na babban zaben shekara ta 2017.
Sai dai, a yanzu haka ba dukkan 'yan jam'iyyar Labour ke goyon bayan wannan kuduri ba.
'Aiki kwana hudu a mako ba manufa ce ta jam'iyya ba kuma ba za a yi tunanin yin hakan ba,' in ji mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour.
Mataimakin Shugaban Majalisar Dattawa, John McDonnell, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don bayyana manufofinsa kan sauya tsarin tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce ya kuduri aniyar dawo da karfin da aka kwace daga 'masu mulki marasa fuska' da kuma 'masu shiga tsakani da kamfanonin ruwa, gas da wutar lantarki.
Shirin na mataimakin shugaban kasa ya kuma nuna cewa abokan hulɗa a cikin kamfanonin samar da ruwa na iya ba da cikakken goyon baya ga shirinsa yayin da gwamnatin ma'aikata ke 'rage kuɗi' bisa laifukan da ta gani.
Ya kuma ba da sanarwar cewa yana shirin sanya ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni da kafa asusun mallakar ma'aikata wanda zai ba da kashi 10 cikin ɗari na hannun jari na kamfanonin da ke da ikon ma'aikata, wanda aka tsara cewa kowane zai iya samun rabon riba har zuwa fam 500.
Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy sun gaya wa "60 Minutes" idan binciken FBI akan Kavanaugh zai iya canza ra'ayinsu.
Binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Alkali Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta har tsawon mako guda a zaben karshe na shugaban kotun koli, kuma an yi tambaya ko binciken hukumar zai iya janye goyon bayan sanatocin Republican.
A wata hira da aka yi a ranar Lahadi, ma'aikacin "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi Sanatocin Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI na iya samun wani abu da zai iya canza tunaninsu.
Kennedy ya fi dacewa da abokin aikinsa na Carolina ta Kudu.
"Hakika haka ne", in ji Kennedy.
"Na yi magana game da zuwa kotu, na yi magana, na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan wannan, na tabbatar da zarginsa, na ce, 'Ka yi haka?'
Ya cika alkawarinsa, ya yi magana da gaba gaɗi kuma ya faɗi abin da ya faru da kyau".
Duk da haka, zaɓen Graham ya zama kamar an tabbatar da shi.
"Na yanke hukunci game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma ina son in yanke hukuncin da ya sabawa tuhumar", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta hakan gaba ɗaya", Graham ya kara da cewa yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma duk wanda ya ce ba zai iya sarrafa shi ba.
Wannan tuhuma ce da ta shafi shekaru 36 da suka gabata.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu da zai canja".
Shin bikin Global Citizen Festival ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara wanda ke nuna manyan mawaƙa da ke da manufa mai ban sha'awa, kawar da talauci a duniya.
Yanzu, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen Festival yana jan dubban mutane zuwa Babban Lawn na Central Park ba kawai don jin daɗin ayyukan manyan masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don yin gwagwarmaya game da ainihin manufar bikin, wato kawar da matsanancin talauci a shekara ta 2030.
An fara bikin bikin na Global Citizen a shekarar 2012 a matsayin wani bangare na shirin Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya mai ba da shawara na kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci da kuma kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa bikin (sai dai idan kuna son biyan kuɗin girmamawa), masu halarta dole ne suyi ayyuka daban-daban ko "ayyuka" kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel ga shugabannin duniya, kira ko wasu hanyoyi masu amfani don taimakawa kamfen ɗin don kawar da talauci.
Amma ta yaya Global Citizen ke ci gaba da ci gaba da wannan aikin idan har yanzu akwai shekaru 12 kafin a cimma burin?
Shin ra'ayin biyan kuɗi don halartar kide kide kyauta hanya ce mai kyau don sa mutane su nemi aiki ko kuma wata hanyar "ƙaddamar da kira ta yanar gizo" ce, inda mutane ke jin cewa za su kawo canji na gaske ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takardar neman izinin yanar gizo ko aika saƙo a Twitter?
Tun daga 2011, cibiyar sada zumunta ta Global Citizen ta ce ta tattara "ayyuka" miliyan 19 da magoya bayanta suka yi, wanda ke haifar da manufofi daban-daban.
Rahoton ya ce, wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da manufofi da manufofi masu darajar dala biliyan 37 da nufin inganta rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta bayyana hakan ta hanyar ƙaddamar da ayyukan 390 tare da ba da gudummawar ko tara aƙalla dala biliyan 10.
Ƙungiyar ta kiyasta cewa tallafin da aka samu ya kawo canji kai tsaye ga mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wasu daga cikin ayyukan sun hada da tuntuɓar The Power of Nutrition, ƙungiyar 'yan kasuwa da masu ba da shawara a Burtaniya waɗanda ke da alhakin "taimaka wa yara su cika damar su", sun ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen kawar da rashin abinci mai gina jiki a ƙasar bayan an sami saƙonnin Twitter sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin jihohi da 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya kawo ƙarshen rashin daidaiton zamantakewar da ke cikin tarihi", in ji jakadan kungiyar The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, ga taron a wani taron kai tsaye a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an gudanar da ayyuka sama da 5,000 don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga iyaye da yara a Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da tallafawa shirin Power of Nutrition, wanda zai shafi mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke da damar samun abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsar da ta bayar ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a dandalinsa, ta ce: "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Global citizen ta amsa: "Zai kasance dogon aiki mai wuya; wani lokacin ya haɗa da faɗuwa da isa ga manufa.
Amma kamar yadda manyan juyin juya halin kare hakkin dan adam da kuma yaki da wariyar launin fata a Afirka ta Kudu suka faru kafin mu fara aiki, za mu cimma nasara, domin idan muka hada kai za mu fi karfi.
Masu kida da suka hada da Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin wadanda za su yi waka a wannan shekara a wani biki da za a yi a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gudanar.
Amurka na iya amfani da jiragen ruwa don "kulle" da hana Rasha aikawa da dakarun kasashen waje, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Washington na iya "idan ya zama dole" yanke shawarar amfani da jiragen ruwan ta don hana iskar gas ta Rasha isa kasuwannin da dama, gami da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya zargi Rasha da shiga tsakani a rikicin Syria; ya tafi ne bisa gayyatar gwamnati ta gaskiya, amma a matsayin uzuri don neman sabon tushen iskar gas.
An ruwaito shi yana cewa: "Na yi imanin cewa dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne don su sami damar samun gas kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai".
Kuma bisa ga abin da hukumomi suka ce, akwai hanyoyin da za a magance su.
Ya ce, "Amurka tana da ikon, ta hanyar jiragen ruwanmu, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku sun bude kuma idan ya cancanta, rufe su, don tabbatar da cewa gas din ba zai isa kasuwa ba".
Zinke ya gabatar da jawabi ga masu halarta taron da aka yi maraba da shi ta ƙungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance, wata ƙungiya mai zaman kanta wacce ta bayyana kanta a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da iskar gas" a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta dabarun da gwamnatin Washington ke amfani da su wajen magance Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa babu wani abu iri daya tsakanin kasashen biyu.
"Zaɓuɓɓukan tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha, kusan, shine samun makamashi da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana nufin cewa Rasha "doki ne mai wayo" wanda tattalin arzikinta ya dogara da man fetur.
Wannan magana ta biyo bayan shirin gwamnatin Trump na kara yawan iskar gas da ake sarrafawa a Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ke samar da gas mai rahusa ga kasashen Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, gami da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna ƙoƙari su rinjayi Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun gas na "rashin nasara" wanda aka kira Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya sa Berlin ta zama "amintaccen" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta ci gaba da ba da shawarar dala biliyan 11 a cikin aikin bututun gas mai suna Nord Stream 2, wanda ake tsammanin zai ninka ƙarfin bututun zuwa mita biliyan 110 na cubic, ba tare da wani dalili ba sai dai don zama aikin tattalin arziki.
Kremlin ya ce rashin amincewar da Washington ta yi da wannan shirin ya dogara ne da dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne mai kyau na nuna tsaka tsaki a cikin gasa ta kasuwa.
"Na yi imanin cewa mun yarda cewa gas ba zai iya zama wani abu na nuna bambanci ba kuma masu amfani da shi dole ne su sami damar zaɓar masu samar da shi", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Wannan matakin na Amurka bai yi kyau ba ga Jamus, wanda ta sake jaddada goyon bayanta ga wannan shirin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta bukaci Amurka da ta guji kusanci da manufofin makamashi na Tarayyar Turai da yarjejeniyar Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta katse mana hanyar samar da iskar gas", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) a wani taron da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi "tunanin gaske" game da neman takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020, kamar yadda Sanatan Massachusetts ya bayyana.
A ranar Asabar, Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce tana bukatar "tunanin gaske" game da neman takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron koli a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin tsayawa takara.
A cewar jaridar The Hill, ta ce: "Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su goyi bayan gwamnatinmu da ta rabu biyu da kuma shugabancin mata".
"Bayan 6 ga watan Disamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da neman takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi tsokaci game da Shugaba Donald Trump a wani taron majalisar dattijai, yana mai cewa yana "jawo kasar cikin hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya sake yin suka kan Trump da kuma wanda ya nada a matsayin shugaban kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
