A ranar Laraba, Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi watsi da yadda jaridar China Daily ta biya jaridar Des Moines Register, babbar jaridar da ke sayar da jaridu a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba, wanda China ta musanta zargin.
Zargin da Trump ya yi wa Beijing na tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fadawa Reuters a matsayin wani mataki na shirin Washington na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Yayin da yake da kyau ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace don tallata kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci wanda ya kai ga ƙarin haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa daga kowace ƙasa.
China ta sake yin martani kan batun haraji a yakin cinikayya da aka shirya yi da masu fitar da kayayyaki daga Iowa da ke tallafawa Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, a cewar wani masani kan dangantakar Sin da Amurka.
