A lokacin da ta fara gabatar da kanta a shirin Desert Island Discs na Radio 4, Lauren Laverne ta ce ta yi magana game da 'yancin maza da mata don ba wasu "bege".
Ta kuma ce kasancewa uwa ta sa ba ta mai da hankali ga samun lambobin yabo a gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin mai tsawo, Kirsty Young, ta dauki hutun watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Da yake bayyana a matsayin wanda aka ƙi a farkon Laverne, Daley ya ce yana jin "ƙananan" ga kowane matashi saboda "ba a yarda da shi a cikin iyali don son yara maza da mata ba".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, wannan rashin mutunci da rashin mutunci na da muhimmanci sosai a gare ni kuma hakan ya sa na sami ƙarfin yin nasara".
Domin ya nuna cewa shi "wani abu ne", ya faɗi haka don kada ya ɓata wa kowa rai sa'ad da ya sami labarin jima'i.
Mai lambar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ya zama sanannen mai fafutukar gay kuma ya yi amfani da halartar wasannin Commonwealth na Ingila da na mulkin mallaka na Ingila a Ostiraliya don yin kira ga ƙasashe da yawa da su dakatar da aikata laifuka ga jima'i tsakanin jinsi ɗaya.
Ya ce ya yi hakan ne saboda yana jin damar samun 'yanci da kuma son ya ba wasu "bege".
Mai cin kofin duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi "mamaki" lokacin da ya sadu da wani ɗan Amurka mai shirya fina-finai, Dustin Lance Black, a 2013.
Daley ta auri wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, a shekarar da ta gabata amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka shiga cikin abubuwa da yawa a cikin ƙuruciyarka", inda ta ce ta halarci gasar Olympics ta farko lokacin da take da shekaru 14 kuma mahaifinta ya mutu daga ciwon kansa bayan kwana uku, ta ce yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya da ya fuskanci irin wannan yanayin.
Ma'auratan sun zama iyaye a watan Yuni, sun haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "duk tunaninsa" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni abin da na fi so a bara, zan ce, 'Ina so in lashe zinare.'"
"Ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare muhimmanci a gasar Olympics.
Robbie ne lambar zinare ta Olympics".
An ba wa ɗansa suna bayan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 bayan an gano shi da cutar kansa ta kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai taba amincewa da cewa zai mutu ba kuma ba ya son tikitin su zuwa wasannin Olympics na 2012 a London, saboda yana son su zauna a gaban fage.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba, 'Baba ba za ka iya zama a gaban fage ba.'"
"Na riƙe hannayensa lokacin da ya yi numfashi na ƙarshe, kuma lokacin da ya yi numfashi na ƙarshe ne na tabbata cewa ya mutu kuma na tabbata cewa ba a kashe shi ba".
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe lambar tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shine burina a rayuwata, yin wasa a gaban 'yan uwan ƙasata a gasar Olympics, babu wani abin da ya fi wannan damuwa", in ji ta.
Wannan ya ba ta ra'ayin waƙar ta farko da ta fi so, Proud by Heather Small, wanda ya zama sananne a ko'ina yayin da take shirin gasar Olympics kuma yana motsa ta ta share tebur.
Za a fara watsa shirye-shiryen Desert Island Discs a ranar Lahadi a karfe 11:15 na safe agogon Burtaniya a tashar BBC Radio 4.
An sanya dan wasan baya Mickelson a matsayin mai maye gurbinsa a gasar cin kofin Ryder a ranar Asabar.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma zai bukaci karin wasanni don kauce wa rashin nasara.
Mickelson, wanda ke buga gasar cin kofin duniya karo na 12, ya zama mataimakin kyaftin Jim Furyk a wasan da ya buga da abokan wasan sa a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon yin aikin yau da kullun kamar yadda ake yi a Amurka, wanda ya ci manyan wasanni biyar yana raba ranarsa ya zama mai maye gurbinsa kuma yana aiki don daidaitawa don gyara abin da ya ɓace.
Ba ta da kyau sosai duk da cewa ta kai matakin farko a rayuwarta, dan wasan mai shekara 48 bai dace da gasar Le Golf National ba, inda masu buga kwallo da ba su da kyau ke shan wahala.
Kuma idan wasan da aka buga bai isa ba, Mickelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, ya yi karo da Francesco Molinari, wanda ya lashe gasar British Open, wanda ya yi wasa da mai farawa Tommy Fleetwood don lashe dukkan wasanninsu huɗu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa, waɗanda ba su da maki huɗu bayan farawa wasanni 12 a jere, suka fara gasar da ƙarfi, wasan Mickelson na iya zama wasa mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa yana da tabbaci a cikin mutumin, ko da yake ba zai iya faɗa ƙarin abubuwa game da mutumin ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Yana da cikakken fahimi game da matsayinsa a yau, sai ya buga ni a baya kuma ya ɗora hannunsa a kafaɗata ya ce yana shirye don gobe".
"Yana da gaba gaɗi sosai.
Yana daya daga cikin fitattun 'yan wasan da ya bayar da gudummawa sosai ga kungiyoyin a kwanakin baya da kuma wannan makon.
Ban taba tunanin cewa zai iya buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na ga abubuwa da yawa, amma yadda suka faru da kuma yadda muka yi tsammani za su faru.
Yana son yin wasa kamar kowa".
Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a matsayin wanda ya fi buga wasa a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Lahadi.
Wannan zai iya zama ƙarshen wasan Ryder Cup wanda ba zai taɓa daidaitawa da nasarar da ya samu a matsayin ɗan wasa ba.
Mickelson ya ci 18, ya sha 20 kuma ya ci kwallaye 7, kodayake Furyk ya ce kasancewa a wurin yana sa ƙungiyar ta zama mai mahimmanci.
Ya ce: "Yana da fara'a, yana jinkiri, yana da basira, yana yawan baƙar magana, kuma mutumin kirki ne da za a so a yi tarayya da shi".
"Ina ganin matasa sun ji daɗin kasancewa tare da shi, kuma wannan makon ya kasance mai kyau a gani.
Yana ba da fiye da wasa".
Kyaftin Turai, Thomas Bjorn, ya san cewa babban matsayi na iya ɓace da sauri.
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Turai, ya san cewa jagorancin da aka samu a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup na iya zama mummunan abu.
Dan wasan ya fara wasan 1997 a Valderrama, inda Seve Ballesteros ya jagoranci ta hanyar maki biyar a gaban Amurkawa amma sun gama da nisa, suna cin nasara 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Kuna iya tuna cewa muna kan gaba a Valderrama; muna kan gaba a Brookline, inda ya sha kashi, kuma a Valderrama, inda ya ci, amma wannan shi ne duka", in ji Bjorn, wanda aka zana a hoton, bayan kallon 'yan wasan 2018 da suka ci 5-3 a wasannin Juma'a da suka gabata da 10-6 a gasar Le Golf National.
Don haka, tarihi zai nuna min da sauran 'yan wasan kungiyar cewa ba a gama ba.
Amma za ka yi amfani da dukan ƙarfinka gobe.
Ka fita ka yi abin da ke daidai.
Ba za a iya kammala ba har sai an rubuta maki a kan allo.
Manufarmu ita ce mu ci kofin, kuma wannan shi ne abin da muke mai da hankali a kai.
Kamar yadda na fada tun da daɗewa, zan iya mai da hankali kan 'yan wasa 12 da ke gefenmu, amma mun san abin da ke gabanmu a gefe ɗaya; manyan' yan wasa a duniya. "
Bjorn ya ci gaba da cewa yana farin ciki da cewa 'yan wasan na sun yi wasa a filin wasan golf mai wahala, "Ba zan iya samun nasara a kaina a wannan gasar ba.
Amma gobe za a yi abubuwa da yawa.
Gobe ne halin mutum wanda dole ne a nuna shi kuma shine bambanci tsakanin abin da ya kamata mu yi.
Yana da kyau a kasance tare da abokin wasan idan abubuwa suna tafiya daidai, amma idan kana wasa da kanka, to sai ka gwada mafi kyawunka a matsayin ɗan wasan golf.
Wannan shine sakon da ya kamata ka tura wa 'yan wasan, wanda shine suyi aiki da kyau gobe.
Saboda haka, sai ka bar abin da ka ke da shi, ka tafi ka yi girbi don kanka da kuma amfanin gona".
Ba kamar Bjorn ba, Jim Furyk zai yi amfani da wasu nau'ikan tufafi don nuna wa 'yan wasansa yadda za su yi wasa da kansu fiye da yadda abokan wasan su suka yi, musamman Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka sami maki uku cikin huɗu.
Furyk da kansa ya kasance a ƙarshen ƙarshen ranar ƙarshe, inda ya kasance ɗaya daga cikin ƙungiyar da ta yi nasara a Brookline kafin ta rasa lokacin da Turai ta janye daga gasar da aka kira "Miracle at Medinah".
"Na tuna da yadda kowace kalma ta yi", in ji shi lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin din kungiyar ta 1999, ya taimaka wa 'yan wasan har zuwa ranar karshe.
"Muna da manyan wasanni 12 gobe, amma dole ne ku fara da sauri kamar yadda kuka gani a Brookline, kamar yadda kuka gani a Medinah.
Idan aka yi amfani da ƙarfi a hanya ɗaya, za a iya ganin matsi a kan 'yan wasa na tsakiya.
Muna sanya 'yan wasan da ke wasa a wasan da kuma fitar da' yan wasan da suka dace da muke tsammanin za mu so, ku sani, muna kokarin yin abubuwan al'ajabi gobe".
An ba Thomas aikin ƙoƙarin jagorantar ƙungiyar don yin gasa da Rory McIlroy a wasan tseren tsere, tare da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter da sauran Turai a farkon matakin gasar.
Bjorn ya ce game da zaɓen 'yan wasa da ke wasa da mutum ɗaya: "Na ɗauki wannan ƙungiyar zuwa mataki na gaba saboda ina tsammanin tana da dukkan' yan wasan da za su amfana".
Sabuwar jirgin ruwan yakin Jamus ya sake canza lokaci
An ba da izinin sabon jirgin ruwan yakin Jamus a cikin 2014 don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwan Cold War, amma ba za a iya samun su ba har zuwa aƙalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingancin tsarin da tsada, a cewar kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An jinkirta izinin shiga teku ga jirgin ruwa mai suna "Rheinland-Pfalz", wanda shine babban jirgin ruwa na sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg, har zuwa farkon 2019, a cewar Die Zeit, wanda ya ambaci wani kakakin soja.
An kuma samu wasu jiragen ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsaloli a cikin jigilar su sun kawo cikas ga wannan babban aikin.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg sune jiragen ruwa da rundunar sojan ruwa ta umarce su a shekarar 2007 don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Tabbas, yana buƙatar samun makamai masu ƙarfi, nau'ikan makamai masu linzami da yawa waɗanda ke kare shi daga harin jirgin sama da na jirgin ruwa da kuma fasahar shiga cikin ruwan abokan gaba ba tare da ɓata lokaci ba, kamar rage hangen nesa na radar, siginar hasken wuta da ji da na'urorin sauti.
Wani muhimmin fasalin jirgin shine cewa ana iya gyara shi bayan dogon lokaci, wanda zai iya sa a sake shigar da sabon jirgin ruwa a cikin teku aƙalla shekaru biyu daga tashar jirgin ruwa ta ƙasar waje.
Duk da haka, jinkirin da ake samu yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa suna da fasaha mai inganci, kamar yadda aka ce zai iya sa Jamus ta kasance mai iko a kan hanyoyin, wanda zai zama mara amfani idan aka fara amfani da shi, in ji Die Zeit.
An sake buga labarin F125 a cikin jaridu a bara, lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi amincewa da jirgin ruwa kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa kamfanin Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne lokaci na farko da rundunar sojan ruwa ta koma da jirgin ruwa ga masana'anta bayan an gyara shi.
Babu wani dalili da ya sa aka mayar da shi, amma jaridun Jamus sun ce akwai wasu manyan kurakurai a cikin "shirye-shiryen da na'urori" da suka sa jirgin ya kasa ɗaukar lokaci mai tsawo don shiga yaƙi.
Musamman, rashin daidaito na shirye-shirye ya kasance mai tsanani yayin da jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki da ƙungiya na ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120, wani ɓangare na ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na tsohuwar jirgin ruwa na Bremen.
Kuma an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana rage ƙarfin sojojin ruwa ta hanyar ƙarin kayan aikin jirgin a nan gaba.
Jirgin ruwan mai nauyin tan 7,000 na Rheinland-Pfalz ya ninka nauyin jirgi mai nauyin jirgi guda biyu da Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga injina da ke da lahani, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya, gami da horar da matuƙan jirgin ruwa, zai zama matsala.
An ce ya kai dala biliyan 3.1 (dala biliyan 3.6), daga dala biliyan 2.2 da aka tsara.
Matsalolin da ke tattare da sababbin nau'ikan jiragen ruwa suna cikin damuwa yayin da ake jin jita-jitar cewa sojojin ruwan Jamus suna raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa rundunar sojan ruwa a halin yanzu "ba ta da jiragen ruwa don kai hari".
"A cikin shekaru da yawa, matsalar ta ƙaru", in ji shi, "saboda tsofaffin jiragen ruwa sun daina tafiya, amma ba a ba da sababbin jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi gunaguni cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da ya isa ya shiga cikin rundunar.
