Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 aka kashe a girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Yayin da tsarin karɓar saƙo da watsawa ya gaza aiki, jami'an aikin ceto ba su sami damar samun saƙo daga yankin Donggala ba, wanda ke arewacin Palu kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
A Palu, an ceto mutane sama da 16,000 bayan da bala'in ya afku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, Sulawesi:
Palu birni ne da ke lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke kusa da gabar teku a yammacin gabar tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da mazaunan kimanin 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin zai tuna da girgizar kasa da tsunami shekaru 40 da suka gabata.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (mil 180) a gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Wannan yanki, wanda shine yanki na yanki, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da kiwo sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki a lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman, a yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma yawancin ayyukan hakar ma'adinai suna cikin Morowali, a wani gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya afkawa yankin Donggala na yamma a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana saman tekun Pacific kuma ana yawan fuskantar girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba, wanda ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, rabin su 'yan Aceh ne.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a bakin tekun Sumatra.
An kashe mutane da yawa a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya lalata gabar teku ta kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku a yankin kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke gabashin Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya haddasa ruwa mai zurfi mita 10 a teku.
2016: Wani ƙaramin girgizar ƙasa ya afku a yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, wanda ya haifar da lalacewa da yawa da kuma fargabar mutane saboda tunatarwa cewa babu tsunami da ya yi mummunan rauni da mutuwar mutane da yawa a 2004.
Babu wata tsunami da ta faru a wannan lokacin, amma sama da mutane 100 ne ambaliyar ta kashe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a tsibirin yawon buɗe ido na Lombok na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido ba tare da gidaje na ɗan lokaci ba.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne saboda zargin cin zarafin mata.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, a kan zargin aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, hana sanarwar cin zarafin mata da kuma kin amincewa da kama shi, a cewar rahoton da jami'an tsaro na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata mace da ta sani ta yi kokarin kiran' yan sanda don bayyana zargin, sai suka kwace wayar ta.
Palin tana tsare a cibiyar Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an ba da belin da ba a tabbatar da shi ba na dala 500, a cewar KTUU.
An gurfanar da shi a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana cewa "ba ya yarda da tuhumar da ake masa" lokacin da aka tambaye shi ko ya yarda da tuhumar, kamar yadda gidan talabijin din ya ruwaito.
Ana tuhumar Palin da laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda ke nufin cewa za a iya yanke masa hukuncin daurin shekara guda da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ya shafi Class B, wanda ake yankewa hukuncin kisa na kwana daya a gidan yari da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da ake tuhumar Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge shi da lalata mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don sanar da ita game da harin.
A halin yanzu ana gurfanar da shi a gaban Kotun Tsohon Sojojin Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin gida, hana bayar da rahoton aikata laifukan gida da kuma kasancewa cikin iko yayin shan barasa dangane da laifin.
Yarinyar da suke so ta so ta buge shi a fuska.
An yi watsi da Sarah Palin daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a 2016 bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da damuwa da ya samu daga yaƙi a Iraki.
