Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya za su nemi hukuncin kisa da ba a saba ba don zargin harin ta'addanci a birnin NYC.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da aikata harin kunar bakin wake a birnin New York wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas; hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar don aikata laifi ga kasa tun 1953.
Ana zargin Saipov, mai shekara 30, da yin amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari kan masu wucewa a kan hanyar West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya buge masu tafiya da keke a kan hanyar a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ya ji rauni mai tsanani "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar neman hukuncin kisa, da aka shigar a Kotun Kudancin New York.
An rubuta cewa waɗannan laifuffukan biyu suna iya jawo hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuffuka 22 da suka hada da mutuwar mutane takwas ta hanyar taimakawa wajen samun kudaden haram, wanda masu gabatar da kara suka yi amfani da shi a shari'ar aikata laifuka da gangan da kuma tuhumar aikata mugunta da lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi da gangan", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayanin yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da "mummunan, mummunan, mummunan hari".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya ji rauni, ya cutar da kuma kashe dangin da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar da aka fitar game da niyyar sa.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda harin ya kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da kotu ta New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kisan wasu masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a wani shari'a a New York ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa bayan an same su da laifin leken asiri ga tsohuwar Tarayyar Soviet shekaru biyu kafin yakin sanyi.
An kashe Rosenbergs da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadamar abin da ya aikata a kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa ya ji dadi sosai game da abin da ya yi, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya yanke shawarar kai harin bayan kallon bidiyon kungiyar ISIS a wayar sa, a cewar wata takarda da ke dauke da tuhumar.
Har ila yau, ya nemi a nuna tutar kungiyar ISIS a dakin jinya, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Ya yi watsi da tuhume-tuhume guda 22 da ake yi masa.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke kare Saipov, ya ce "ba shi da farin ciki" da hukuncin da ake yi.
"Muna ganin cewa hukuncin kisa ne maimakon hukuncin da aka yanke masa na yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai ba tare da wata dama ba, wanda zai kara damun duk wanda ke da hannu a lamarin", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar da ke kare Saipov ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da su guji yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Tory ya ce ya kamata a baiwa Nigel Farage aikin tattauna yadda za a fice daga kungiyar tarayyar Turai.
Nigel Farage ya kuduri aniyar 'karfafa mutane' a zanga-zangar da aka yi a yau a gaban taron jam'iyyar Tory.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su fito daga cikin inuwar 'yan adawa da kungiyar tarayyar Turai, inda wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Theresa May ya ce ya kamata ya zama shugaban tattaunawar da kungiyar tarayyar Turai.
Wani dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya, Peter Bone, ya shaida wa masu ziyara a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "ta fice daga kungiyar" yanzu da Mr Farage ya zama Sakataren Ficewar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai.
Amma matsalar da Ms May ke fuskanta ita ce hada kan abokan aikinta masu ra'ayi daban-daban don sa 'yan Tory da ke son ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU su shiga zanga-zangar da ke nuna rashin amincewarsu da ficewar Burtaniya daga EU a birane.
Firaministan na fama da matsalar ganin an cimma manufar ficewar Birtaniya daga kungiyar tarayyar Turai a yayin da yake fuskantar matsin lamba daga masu neman ficewar Birtaniya da kuma masu son ci gaba da kasancewa a kungiyar.
Abokan hulɗarsu sun ci gaba da cewa zai ci gaba da ƙoƙarin yin sulhu da Belgium duk da rashin jin daɗin da aka samu, kuma sun matsa masa ya soki EU da Labour don yanke shawarar da ya yanke.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa masu halartar taron 'Leave Means Leave' a Solihull cewa yana son 'dakatar da shirin Birtaniya na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai'.
Ya ce dole ne a hada da Mista Farage kuma a ba shi aikin tattaunawa da Belgium.
Domin sun ce, 'Da wannan mutumin ne ya yi mulkin, da mun riga mun fita daga nan.'
'Zan yi gwagwarmaya don Birtaniya ta fice daga EU amma muna bukatar a soke shirin Birtaniya na ficewa daga EU,' in ji dan majalisar Wellingborough.
Da yake magana game da matsayinsa game da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙe - yaƙe na duniya don nuna rashin ƙarfi ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokoki a ƙasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da muradin jama'a tun bayan zaben 2016: 'Ra'ayin cewa 'yan Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son kasancewa cikin iyali ba gaskiya bane.'
'Yar jam'iyyar Tory da ke son Birtaniya ta fice daga Tarayyar Turai, Andrea Jenkyns, wacce ita ma ta halarci wannan ziyara, ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: 'Abin da kawai nake so in fada shi ne: Firaminista, ka saurari jama'a.
'Manufar ficewar Birtaniya daga EU ba ta da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su kada kuri'a ba, ba ta da kyau a jam'iyyarmu kuma masu kawo sauyi da muke aiki tare da su a kan tituna ne suka sa aka zabe mu a farkon wuri.
