Sashin 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge ya sanar da cewa sun kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, da misalin karfe 11 na safe agogon Gabas, kamar yadda aka ruwaito a cikin wani rahoto.
Sun fitar da bidiyon harin da aka yi ranar Juma'a, suna neman taimako kan wanda aka nuna a hoton.
An harbe Sims, mai shekara 20, a kusa da Jami'ar Southern a safiyar ranar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya mutu ne sakamakon wata harbin bindiga da aka yi masa a kai kuma ya mutu a wurin da aka harbe shi", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul, a wata sanarwa da 247sports ta fitar a ranar Asabar.
Wayde ya zo ne domin ya ceci abokinsa kuma Simpson ya kashe shi.
Simpson ya amsa tambayoyin kuma ya yarda cewa yana da bindiga a wurin harbi kuma ya yarda da harbin Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wata matsala ba kuma an kai shi ofishin 'yan sanda na yankin East Baton Rouge.
Wani ƙaramin yaro mai tsayi 6ft 2in wanda ya ci gaba a Baton Rouge, Sims ya buga wasanni 32 inda ya fara 10 a kakar wasa ta bara kuma ya yi ta yin kimanin minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da kuma sake dawowa 2.9 a kowane wasa.
