Gasar Elite League: Dundee Stars ta doke Belfast Giants da ci 5-3
Patrick Dwyer ya ci wa Giants kwallo biyu a karawar da suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars ta sauya rashin nasarar da ta samu a gasar Elite ta ranar Juma'a lokacin da ta ci wasan cin kofin zakarun Belfast da ci 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci kwallo biyu a farkon wasan da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka buga.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun jagoranci tawagar zuwa raga kafin Dwyer ya sake jagoranci Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya ci kwallo biyu a raga a wasan da Dundee ta yi kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci kwallo biyu a raga.
Wannan shine nasara ta uku a gasar Elite a kakar wasa ta Adam Keefe, wanda ya ci Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a daren Juma'a.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu a kakar wasa da kungiyoyin biyu suka hadu, inda Giants suka lashe wasanninsu uku.
Dwyer ya fara bugawa kungiyar kwallo a minti na uku da rabi a hannun Kendall McFaull, inda David Rutherford ya ba Beauvillier kwallon da ta ci ta biyu a minti kadan.
A wani abu da ya bayyana a matsayin babban farawa, Sullivan ya dawo da kungiyar a wasa a minti 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya ba Cownie kwallon da ta zira kwallo a minti 15:16.
Dwyer ya ci gaba da jagorantar Giants a wasan farko ta hanyar zira kwallaye biyu na wasan na dare a ƙarshen rabin wasa.
Kungiyar da ta karbi bakuncin wasan ta sake buga wasan kuma Bouchard ya sake zira kwallo a raga a minti na 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen ya baiwa Dundee damar daukar ragamar farko a wasan kafin karshen rabin wasa kuma ya sa tawagar ta ci wasan a minti na karshe.
Giants, wanda yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da ya buga, zai ziyarci Milton Keynes a wasa na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
