Wani mai bincike ya nuna lokacin dare mace ta kone da rai
Masu gabatar da kara sun gabatar da kara a ranar Asabar don sake gurfanar da wani mutum da ake zargi da kona wata mata a Mississippi da rai a shekarar 2014.
A ranar Laraba, Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka Paul Rowlett ta ba da shaida na tsawon sa'o'i a matsayin mashawarcin gwani a cikin binciken leken asiri na aikata laifuka.
Ya bayyana wa kotu yadda ya yi amfani da wayar salula don samun bayanan tafiye-tafiye da aka yi tsakanin wanda ake tuhuma, Quinton Tellis, mai shekara 29, da wanda aka kashe, Jessica Chambers, mai shekara 19, a daren da aka kashe shi.
Rowlett ya ce ya karɓi bayanan wuri daga wayoyi daban-daban waɗanda suka nuna cewa Tellis yana tare da Chambers a daren da ya mutu, wanda ya bambanta da abin da ya gabata, a cewar The Clarion Ledger.
Lokacin da rahotanni suka nuna cewa wayar salula ta kasance a hannun Chambers yayin da ta ce tana tare da abokinta Michael Sanford, 'yan sanda sun tuntubi Sanford.
Sanford ya je wurin da aka yi wa'azi a ranar Asabar kuma ya ba da shaida cewa ba ya cikin gari a ranar.
Lokacin da masu gabatar da kara suka tambayi ko Tellis zai kasance da gaskiya lokacin da ya ce yana cikin motar Sanford a daren, Sanford ya ce "yana ƙarya, saboda motarsa tana Nashville".
Wani labarin da ya sabawa wannan ra'ayi shi ne cewa Tellis ya ce ya san Chambers kusan makonni biyu bayan mutuwarsa.
Bayanan wayar salula sun nuna cewa sun san juna ne har tsawon mako guda.
Rowlett ya ce jim kadan bayan mutuwar Chambers, Tellis ya share sakonnin Chambers, da kiran waya da kuma adireshin mahaifinsa daga wayarsa.
Hale ya ce, "Ya bar ta a rayuwarsa".
Ana sa ran wanda ake tuhuma zai gabatar da hukuncinsa a ranar Lahadi.
Alkalin kotun ya ce ana sa ran za a yanke hukunci a gaban kotu a cikin sa'o'i na yammacin ranar.
