Ta yaya cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China za ta kasance mai kyau ga Beijing?
Yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya rufe kunnuwan mutane kuma idan har ba a kawo karshen yakin ba, rashin jituwa tsakanin kasashen biyu na iya zama ga amfanin Beijing na dogon lokaci, a cewar masana.
