An sake samun mummunan yanayi a cikin ko kusa da bakin teku na Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan yanayi da yanayin sama a cikin Hillsborough County, mummunan yanayi a cikin Manatee County, inda ya fi dacewa da yanayin cikin ko kusa da bakin teku na Sarasota County, mummunan yanayi a cikin Charlotte County, mummunan yanayi a cikin Lee County da mummunan yanayi a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun matsalar rashin isasshen iska a lardunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Ba a samu rahoton cutar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
